WEBVTT

00:04:58.413 --> 00:05:02.961
(Music)

00:05:06.092 --> 00:05:12.065
If you do nothing else
but to cultivate that response

00:05:12.089 --> 00:05:16.277
to the great gift that this unique day is,

00:05:17.478 --> 00:05:23.904
if you learn to respond
as if it were the first day in your life

00:05:23.928 --> 00:05:26.610
and the very last day,

00:05:26.634 --> 00:05:31.696
then you will have spent
this day very well.